  "detailed_description": "<h1>SiNKR 3</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.poster.avif?t=1761147405\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.webm?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.mp4?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SiNKR is a minimalist puzzler. There is just you, hooks, pucks, and various contraptions you need to finish each level. Sink all the pucks to advance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each level is handcrafted <br></li><li>No scores, no timers, no text, no distractions <br></li><li>Responsive ambient music <br></li><li>Cross platform cloud saves <br></li><li>Full controller support <br></li><li>Steam achievements </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.poster.avif?t=1761147405\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.webm?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.mp4?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.poster.avif?t=1761147405\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.webm?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/0ae30800cb7b24d537316847aeebc3a5.mp4?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SiNKR is a minimalist puzzler. There is just you, hooks, pucks, and various contraptions you need to finish each level. Sink all the pucks to advance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each level is handcrafted <br></li><li>No scores, no timers, no text, no distractions <br></li><li>Responsive ambient music <br></li><li>Cross platform cloud saves <br></li><li>Full controller support <br></li><li>Steam achievements </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.poster.avif?t=1761147405\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.webm?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/676420/extras/1d7b0dced022f11b8de3b20d9e268131.mp4?t=1761147405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
